high_descs: Turn left, go towards the coffee maker, turn left go to the dishwasher on the right.
Take the yellow handle knife from the counter behind the bread.
Cut the bread into slices.
Stay at the counter.
Put the knife on the counter in front of the bread and spatula.
Stay at the counter.
Take a slice of bread from the counter.
Turn left, go to the white refrigerator.
Put the bread in the refrigerator on the shelf with the potato in front of the bowl. Close then open the fridge door. Take the bread from the fridge.
Turn right, go in front of the oven.
Put the bread in the microwave above the oven.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold slice of bread in the microwave.

high_descs: Go as far as you can to your left, then turn left again and continue to the counter to the right of the fridge.
Pick up the knife behind the loaf of bread on the counter.
Slice the right half of the loaf of bread.
Move one step to the right.
Put the knife on the counter, in front of the bread and spatula, parallel to the edge of the counter
Go back one step to the left.
Remove leftmost slice of bread, from near the center of the loaf.
Take the bread slice to the refrigerator on your left.
Put the bread on the middle of the center refrigerator shelf and close the refrigerator, then open it and take the bread slice back out and close the door.
Move to your right to stand facing the stove.
Put the slice of bread into the microwave above the stove.
anns.task_desc: Put a freshly sliced piece of bread into the microwave.

high_descs: Turn to your left and walk to the toaster next to the refrigerator.
Pick up the knife from the counter.
Cut the loaf of bread.
Move one step to your right.
Place the knife on the counter.
Walk one step to the left.
Pick up a slice of bread from the middle of the loaf.
Walk over to the refrigerator.
Open the fridge and place the bread inside and then shut the fridge briefly before opening it again and picking up the slice of bread.
Walk over to the microwave above the stove.
Place the slice of bread inside the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled slice of bread into the microwave.
